      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BIANCA'S SECRET (2) is racing well without winning, recording three minors on end, the latest when checked in the run and finishing second in a Grade 5 at this track (23.43). Should be in this for a long way. CAWBOURNE LADY (1) has been hard to follow lately, running fifth (31.16) last time but prior to that ran very well when placed at this track. Can hit the frame this time. GRAPEFRUIT YAEKO (4) was prominent early from the tricky draw and stalked the lead before levelling up to score (22.38) at Shepparton in a Maiden over 390m. Won at her only start from this box. Form should stack up. LET'S GO JILL (8) is in form and must include among the chances.",
